      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a cool way to put it. \"molecular dance\" makes it sound a lot more organized than it actually is. what happens if the temperature isn't controlled perfectly? like, if it gets too high or if the moisture content is off, does the whole reaction just fall apart or go totally different?",
